fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.io.processor

Class AbstractProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.io.processor.AbstractProcessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    InputHandler, InputNotifier<PersistenceHandler>, Processor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EcoreProcessor, XPathProcessor

    public class AbstractProcessor
extends Object
implements Processor
    An abstract implementation of an Processor that delegates all methods to its embedded processor.
